      <h1>Next Steps</h1>
      <p>Now that you have the basics down, it's really (and I mean, REALLY) important that you take the time to develop a solid mental health routine.</p>
      <p>What does this actually mean? Well, it means developing a practice routine of daily meditation that you can practice each day.</p>
      <p>An important thing to note about porn addiction recovery is that it's not a matter of "knowing" what it's all about, and then you're sudden relieved of ever thinking about porn or masturbation again.</p>
      <p>It is a hard process of committing to practices and exercises which will slowly train your brain not to pursue these self-destructive behaviours.</p>
      <p>Which is to say that without practice, literally nothing will improve and you'll continue to falter. So head on down to the <a href="/meditation" class="link">NeverFap Deluxe Meditation</a> section and understand the verifiable steps you need to take each day.</p>
      <p>In order to ensure effective change in your life. Pronto. Now.</p>
